g.text: Uploading Metadata to an Existing Dataset
type the url of the TRSA
select a row (Dataset) and click its "Select" button
response: "Upload and Ingest a File" page
select a file to be ingested
save the file in a tmp directory
response: the name of the uploaded file returned
ingest the file and save metadata and data themselves
click the check icon in Column "Modify"
